THE ROLE
Expand all
Our client is one of the leading hospital in Abu Dhabi is currently seeking to recruit an Instructional Designer. This position will be based in Abu Dhabi
Job Summary
This position is responsible for assisting in the daily activities associated with the organizational learning and performance services initiated at the Company. This position is also responsible for developing, customizing and maintaining moderately complex training programs and related materials in support of employee training objectives
Primary Duties and Responsibilities
Facilitates the development , customization, support and maintenance of all on-boarding and training programs
Provides instructional support to all employees involved in educational development programs
Demonstrate and utilizes effective needs analysis , course development and evaluation skills
Collaborate with internal peers and personnel to create learning and educational programs and services that positively impact companyâs recruitment and retention strategies
Conduct training sessions and develops criteria for evaluating the effectiveness of training activities
Plans, support and provides administrative support for various projects with the Company
Conducts research into new training, educational and multimedia technologies
REQUIREMENTS
Experience Requirements:
Minimum of ( 2) two years experience as an instructional designer and facilitator is required
Knowledge of theories of adult education
Knowledge of online teaching and learning methods
Exposure to learning management systems
Knowledge of technical writing , performance measuring and multi media course development
Demonstrated competence with Microsoft Office and other PC applications
Strong oral and written communication skills
Demonstrated ability to work effectively with a variety of professional personnel
ABOUT THE COMPANY
Manpower is the global leader in contingent and permanent staffing, helping organizations and job seekers succeed by connecting the potential of people with the ambitions of business. Manpower helps find and retain top people in IT, accounting, banking, finance, legal, engineering, sales and marketing.
